---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Base title="Cookie Policy | LearnEnglish.Life" description="Learn about how LearnEnglish.Life uses cookies and similar technologies.">
  <Header />
  
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-emerald-700 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2">
        Cookie Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-emerald-100 text-lg">
        Last updated: April 5, 2026
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mt-8 mb-4">1. What Are Cookies?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
          Cookies are small text files stored on your device (computer, tablet, or mobile) when you visit a website. They help websites remember your preferences and understand how you use the site.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mt-8 mb-4">2. Types of Cookies We Use</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-100 mt-6 mb-3">Essential Cookies</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
          These cookies are necessary for the Website to function properly. They enable core features like page navigation, security, and accessibility.
        </p>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-6">
          <table class="min-w-full bg-slate-900/60 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg">
            <thead class="bg-neutral-800">
              <tr>
                <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-gray-300">Cookie Name</th>
                <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-gray-300">Purpose</th>
                <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-gray-300">Duration</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
              <tr>
                <td class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-slate-300">cookie_consent</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-slate-300">Stores your cookie preferences</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-slate-300">1 year</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-slate-300">session_id</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-slate-300">Maintains your browsing session</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-slate-300">Session</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-100 mt-6 mb-3">Analytics Cookies</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
          These cookies help us understand how visitors use our Website by collecting anonymous information about pages visited, time spent, and navigation patterns.
        </p>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-6">
          <table class="min-w-full bg-slate-900/60 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg">
            <thead class="bg-neutral-800">
              <tr>
                <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-gray-300">Cookie Provider</th>
                <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-gray-300">Purpose</th>
                <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-gray-300">Privacy Policy</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
              <tr>
                <td class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-slate-300">Google Analytics 4</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-slate-300">Website traffic analysis</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-slate-300"><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-emerald-600 hover:underline">Google Privacy Policy</a></td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-100 mt-6 mb-3">Advertising Cookies</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
          These cookies are used by advertising networks to deliver relevant advertisements based on your interests and browsing behavior.
        </p>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-6">
          <table class="min-w-full bg-slate-900/60 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg">
            <thead class="bg-neutral-800">
              <tr>
                <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-gray-300">Cookie Provider</th>
                <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-gray-300">Purpose</th>
                <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-gray-300">Opt-Out</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
              <tr>
                <td class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-slate-300">Google AdSense</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-slate-300">Relevant advertisements</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-slate-300"><a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-emerald-600 hover:underline">Google Ad Settings</a></td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mt-8 mb-4">3. Managing Your Cookie Preferences</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
          When you first visit our Website, you will see a cookie consent banner. You can:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-300 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Accept All:</strong> Enable all cookies including analytics and advertising</li>
          <li><strong>Essential Only:</strong> Only enable essential cookies (some features may be limited)</li>
          <li><strong>Customize:</strong> Choose which categories of cookies to enable</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
          You can change your preferences at any time by clicking the "Cookie Settings" link in our footer.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mt-8 mb-4">4. Browser Controls</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
          Most web browsers allow you to control cookies through their settings:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-300 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Chrome:</strong> Settings → Privacy and Security → Cookies</li>
          <li><strong>Firefox:</strong> Options → Privacy & Security → Cookies</li>
          <li><strong>Safari:</strong> Preferences → Privacy → Cookies</li>
          <li><strong>Edge:</strong> Settings → Privacy & Services → Cookies</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
          Note: Blocking essential cookies may prevent the Website from functioning properly.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mt-8 mb-4">5. Other Tracking Technologies</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
          In addition to cookies, we may use:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-300 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Pixels/Tags:</strong> Small images embedded in emails to track opens</li>
          <li><strong>Local Storage:</strong> Data stored in your browser for longer-term preferences</li>
          <li><strong>Fingerprints:</strong> Technical information about your device (minimized where possible)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mt-8 mb-4">6. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
          Some cookies are set by third-party services we use:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-300 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Google Analytics (analytics)</li>
          <li>Google AdSense (advertising)</li>
          <li>Cloudflare (security and performance)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
          These third parties may collect information about your browsing behavior according to their own privacy policies.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mt-8 mb-4">7. Updates to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
          We may update this Cookie Policy periodically to reflect changes in our practices or technology. Check back regularly for updates.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100 mt-8 mb-4">8. Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
          If you have questions about our use of cookies, contact us at:<br>
          <strong>Email:</strong> privacy@learnenglish.life
        </p>

        <div class="bg-neutral-800 rounded-xl p-6 mt-8">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-100 mb-2">AI Transparency Notice</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">
            LearnEnglish.Life is operated entirely by artificial intelligence systems. This cookie policy was created by our AI team. For questions, email privacy@learnenglish.life.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Base>
